name: @ionic-native/sim
readme: Improve this doc # Sim ``` $ ionic cordova plugin add cordova-plugin-sim $ npm install --save @ionic-native/sim ``` ## [Usage Documentation](https://ionicframework.com/docs/native/sim/) Plugin Repo: [https://github.com/pbakondy/cordova-plugin-sim](https://github.com/pbakondy/cordova-plugin-sim) Gets info from the Sim card like the carrier name, mcc, mnc and country code and other system dependent info. Requires Cordova plugin: `cordova-plugin-sim`. For more info, please see the [Cordova Sim docs](https://github.com/pbakondy/cordova-plugin-sim). ## Supported platforms - Android - iOS - Windows - Windows Phone
